title: An Obvious Bait
body:
Hey guys, I'm a new youtuber and would really appreciate it if you guys could take a look at some of my work. I mainly do League videos, poking fun at the stupid shit that goes on in bronze. 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EoHt5MiLUIk&index=3&list=PLqUYUFc4BUZAIoEu7JcQ3xh3dMhiHypb9{{champion:119}}

replies.body: The video quality is actually really great and I wouldn't mind be in one of them. I'm bronze aswell if that's a perk
Thank you sir, yeah mate that would be cool. give us an add on league when you're ready and I will see if i can set something up.
